OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA fine day with light winds and
OL,6,Fplenty of sunshine, although
OL,7,Fconditions may become locally hazy
OL,8,Fduring the afternoon. Turning very
OL,9,Fwarm or locally hot inland, but cooler
OL,10,Falong the coast as an onshore breeze
OL,11,Fdevelops.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FAnother warm night for many,
OL,14,Fespecially in urban areas and cities,
OL,15,Fwhile rural locations become
OL,16,Fnoticeably cooler. Dry with light
OL,17,Fwinds and largely clear skies
OL,18,Fthroughout.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
