OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FAnother hot day, dry and
OL,6,Fpredominantly sunny but the odd
OL,7,Fafternoon shower possible, mostly over
OL,8,Fhills. Cooler along coastal areas,
OL,9,Fwith an onshore breeze.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FDry
OL,12,Fand largely sunny, though cooler, on
OL,13,FSaturday. Low cloud and patchy drizzle
OL,14,Fpossible early Sunday before brighter
OL,15,Fconditions develop. Dry with plenty of
OL,16,Fsunshine on Monday, though turning
OL,17,Fcooler.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
